00:41:03,563 --> 00:41:05,648
Agora Erika.

373
00:41:05,649 --> 00:41:08,149
Muito bem, Asia.

374
00:41:08,151 --> 00:41:10,779
-Ótimo!
-Genial!

375
00:41:11,571 --> 00:41:14,783
Encha. Que esta será incrível.

376
00:41:18,203 --> 00:41:21,581
1, 2, 3, 4,

377
00:41:21,832 --> 00:41:25,710
